unisDot11WIPSDctStaVendor OBJECT-TYPE
    SYNTAX OCTET STRING (SIZE (0..127))
    MAX-ACCESS read-only
    STATUS current
    DESCRIPTION
        "Represents the vendor of the station detected by WIPS."
